WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:11.688
StatePort is a harness for coding agents. It runs agents like Codex
StatePort is a harness for coding agents. It runs agents like Codex headlessly, in an environment you control, and gives the work a durable home outside the chat. Here is the preview.

00:00:12.138 --> 00:00:23.871
This is the application you get. Open a named project and see what is
This is the application you get. Open a named project and see what is happening, what needs attention, and what the agent last did. Your state files and decisions live here, not hidden inside a session.

00:00:24.321 --> 00:00:36.177
This is the conversation. You can ask the agent for help, but the
This is the conversation. You can ask the agent for help, but the conversation is only one part of the project. The agent is a replaceable processor — the work does not live or die with the chat.

00:00:36.627 --> 00:00:46.261
